<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="such-that-as-to">such that / as to</h1>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.<strong>到如此程度以致：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>The force of the explosion was such that windows were blown out.
爆炸的力量如此之大，以致窗户都被震碎了。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>The pain in my foot wasn’t such as to stop my walking.
我脚疼，但还不至于不能行走。</p></div>

<p>注: 与不定冠词连用时，such要放在不定冠词之前；与no, all, many, one, few, several, some, any等连用时，则放在其后。  </p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>such a proposal 
那样的建议</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>I made no such decision. 
我没有作过那样的决定。</p></div></div>